{"tid":493255,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方冚賭爬窗走 3賭客跳落地四散1人困簷篷被捕","createTime":"2017-12-08T10:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T11:07:08.000Z","uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"edac182598d78c2e421ff2d06c79f57eb5b3b2c8","tid":493255,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T10:23:57.000Z","msg":"昨晚上近8時，警方在旺角道近通菜街一大廈進行反賭博行動，4名懷疑賭客男子，從二樓窗口爬出，經冷氣機位走到簷篷位置，其中3人迅速跳落地面逃去，惟一名戴眼鏡的黑衫男子，未敢跳下，一度困在簷篷進退不得。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/12/07/3500011/20171207_ccm_01V16_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F3500011%2F20171207_ccm_01V16_w.mp4&d=wssAKdJ35NzKT%2FL3zHh8%2FOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=d019d60d\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/12/07/3500011/20171207_ccm_01V16_w.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n其時街上途人眾多，均嚇得爭相走避，不少人更在附近行人天橋駐足圍觀。讀者黃先生當時在現場，指4名可疑人均年約20至30歲，其中3人首先跳落地往通菜街方向逃走，現場氣氛相當緊張。<br />\n警員接報趕到，一度手持伸縮警棍與困在簷篷位置的男子對峙，並一度大聲喝止對方：「企定定唔好郁呀」，阻止對方跳下。警員更一度爬梯，將對方帶返地面，拘捕帶署調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171207/57554044\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171207%2F57554044&d=wssAKdJ35NzKT%2FL3zHh8%2FOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=d5db44b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171207%2F57554044&h=2da8bcf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171207/57554044</a>"},{"pid":"637faec3831182af440202ab5212afba984f9535","tid":493255,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T10:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eea15c820696d33485e6d3b99aacf1a5b60edcd","tid":493255,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi